The most decadent Gluten Free Chocolate Cake is here for you! The best part is it’s made with ingredients you probably have at home already and it comes together effortlessly thanks to the Prestige zenith blender mixer grinder! 
@ttkprestige 
Ingredients-
80 g oats (ground into a flour) 
1/4 cup milk 
80 g castor sugar 
15 g cocoa powder 
3/4 tsp baking powder 
1/2 tsp baking soda 
25 g oil 
1 tsp vanilla 
3 tbsp. water 
1/2 tsp coffee powder 
1/2 tbsp. vinegar 

Bake in a pre heated 170 degree oven for 25-30 mins or till a toothpick comes out clean.
